title: Cafe Eighteen
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Fast food, Take-out, British, English, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Local coffee house, previous known as The Olive Coffee House and Kitchen. Offers some vegan items including veggie burger, breakfast, sandwiches, salads, ciabatta toast with olives, hummus, nut-free pesto. Food is made to order. Has a vegan alert button on the till to alert the kitchen staff of all vegan orders. Holds Sunday lunch events.
